<title>ạ̉ḥbk mʿny̱ kl wjwd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉ḥbk mʿny̱ kl wjwd .. wạḥbk wạlklạm mḥdwd)2
 wḥbk ʿdy̱ kl sdwd .. (ḥbyby yạ yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 2- (ạ̉ḥbk tnthy ạlậlạmạt .. wạḥbk tbtdy ạlngẖmạt)2
 wḥbk ḥb llnhạyạt .. (ḥbyby yạ yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 3- (ạ̉ḥbk rb llạ̹nsạn .. wạḥbk rạḥẗ llḥyrạn)2
 wḥbk rạyẗ llạ̹ymạn .. (ḥbyby yạ yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 4- (ạ̉ḥbk fwq ṣlyb ạlʿạr .. wạḥbk byn lhyb ạlnạr)2
 wḥbk ḥb llạ̉srạr .. (ḥbyby yạ yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 5- (ạ̉ḥbk ạlqsạwẗ tdwb .. wạḥbk trfʿ ạlmgẖlwb)2
 wḥbk kẖly qlby ytwb .. (ḥbyby yạ yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 6- (ạ̉ḥbk ạ̹nt ạ̉wfy̱ ṣdyq .. wạḥbk ḥty̱ lw fy ạlḍyq)2
 wḥbk lyã ạ̉ʿẓm sẖyʾ .. (ḥbyby yạ yswʿ ạlbạr)</lyrics>
